39c6b514c8","tid":2320060,"uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:05:05.000Z","msg":"兩個治療階段,各留宿3 日2 夜<br />\n六日喎"},{"pid":"945ff3414810d9a7038b9b58e840c653c2765202","tid":2320060,"uid":57531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb56f6a77bc5c4ca1b259083042113751985904b","tid":2320060,"uid":4052,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:57:33.000Z","msg":"試藥死咗果啲人上唔到嚟講啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊有咁大隻蛤乸隨街跳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:08:36.000Z","msg":"survivorship"},{"pid":"00cb1a715eb3bef3818893e56b7fbebd9cfbe4d6","tid":2320060,"uid":248660,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"簡單D即係做白老鼠囉<br />\n係既, D藥試咗好耐, 老鼠無事, 理論上安全, 但係...理論同實際有分別.<br />\n<strong>老鼠</strong>無事, <strong>理論上</strong>安全唔代表應用響人身上安全,<br />\nD人成日問有咩副作用, 其實無人知, 就係有人試完藥出黎先至知有咩問題,有預計到既問題, 亦有預計之外既問題. <br />\n好彩既就噁心,食慾不振, 頭暈, 頭痛咁; 唔好彩既永久傷害(e.g. 肝, 腎, 腦, 生殖器) 都唔定, 長期副作用更加唔知.<br />\n放心,有事實會醫返你既, 不過唔係樣樣傷害可以返轉頭), 最嚴重當然係死啦, (又當然, 你可能話我作大啦).<br />\n基於以上咁多未知, 所以出一萬大洋引人去幫手試藥啦~無話cheap 唔cheap, 你覺得值咪去囉~"},{"pid":"e789b6808a45711999fa3b0db686aff944119481","tid":2320060,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2c5a7d8656c0256fb42a924587f1f8a10ae5a5","tid":2320060,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:24:50.000Z","msg":"全職做呢啲，月薪十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85935d63091f9046b9d29cff8eb3b32ed32154c2","tid":2320060,"uid":84619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"呢個計劃應該捉撚哂班綜緩新移